@REMARK***********************************************************************
@NODE l_general "General information about the 01/W"

  @{u}Technical specifications of the Kork 01/W@{uu}

 * A1 Square-Synthesis-System, @{i}non-linear AI˛-Synthesis-System@{ui}
 * Single mode: @{b}32 Voices@{ub}, 32 Oszillators
 * Double mode: 16 Voices, 32 Oszillators
 * Keyboard: @{b}61 Keys@{ub}, Initial & Aftertouch
 * PCM ROM: @{b}48 MBit@{ub} (@{"255 Multisounds" LINK l_multisounds}, @{"119 Drumsounds" LINK l_drumsounds})
 * Wave Shaping Envelope Generator: @{"60 Effects" LINK l_waveshaping}
 * 2 Stereo-Digital-Multieffect-Processors: @{"47 Effects" LINK l_effects}
 * Programs: 200
 * Combinations: 200
 * Drumkits: 4
 * Sequenzer: 10 songs, 100 patterns, 7000 notes, @{b}16 tracks@{ub}, 16 timbres
 * Input devices: sustain pedal, pedal 1,2
 * Output devices: 1/L, 2/R, 3, 4, earphones
 * PCM-Cards: PCM DATA, PROG/SEQ
 * MIDI: IN, OUT, THRU
 * Display: @{b}LCD 240×64 pixel@{ub}, dot-matrix, background illumination
 * Current consumption: 20 W
 * Measurement: 1059,5 (W) × 334 (D) × 115,5 (H)
 * Weight: 13,4 Kg
@ENDNODE
