@REMARK***********************************************************************
@NODE l_tips "did you know that ..."

 * @{u}load original combinations and programs out of ROM:@{uu}
   go into Globalmode, Page7: PRELOAD >ROM
   load Combi/Prog, Bank-A+B -> Bank-A+B

 * @{u}Version number of ROM:@{uu}
   keep button RESET pressed while turning on the synth

@ENDNODE
